name: Development Machine - Microsoft
tagline: Development Machine for Microsoft environment setup repository
body:
### Welcome to Development Machine for Microsoft environment.
This is a Microsoft Development environment quick setup using the following tools: 
*  Vagrant
*  Packer.IO
*  Boxstarter

```
$ cd CyMadigan/DevelopmentMachine
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Authors and Contributors
In 2015, Cyril Madigan (@CyMadigan) created DevelopmentMachine.
